Seq3.ReceiverContent: Hi, you have reached the nurse line. Please, if this is a medical emergency, please hang up and dial 9-1-1. If you are calling for medication refills today, please leave me a detailed message with the name of your drug and the milligrams and what pharmacy you would like it called into. Leave your name and date of birth. I will get back to you when I can. Please allow 24 to 72 hours for all medication refills. Leave me a message, and I'll get to you as soon as I can. Have a blessed day.
